          <title>

          <description>

            <string language="en">Dam used to provide water to Levtik\'s water mill that is located by the river Bistrica in Podsreda, Kozjansko.</string>

            <string language="x-mt-de">Verdammung verwendete, Wasser zum 
Wassertausendstel Levtik\s zur Verfügung zu stellen, das durch den 
Fluß Bistrica in Podsreda, Kozjansko ist.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le barrage fournissait l'eau au moulin à eau de 
Levtik\ qui est situé près du fleuve Bistrica dans Podsreda, 
Kozjansko.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">A represa usou-se fornecer a água ao moinho de 
água de Levtik\ que é ficado situado pelo rio Bistrica em Podsreda, 
Kozjansko.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">La diga ha usato fornire l'acqua al laminatoio di
acqua del Levtik\ che è situato dal fiume Bistrica in Podsreda, 
Kozjansko.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Φράγμα που χρησιμοποιείται για να παρέχει το ύδωρ στον
υδρόμυλο Levtik\ που βρίσκεται από τον ποταμό Bistrica σε 
Podsreda, Kozjansko.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">La presa proporcionaba al agua al molino de agua 
de Levtik\ que es situado por el río Bistrica en Podsreda, Kozjansko.</string>
